KC-46 capable at an airfield with unmatched air-road-rail 16
intermodal capabilities positioning Rickenbacker to be a 17
strategic aerial port of embarkation; and 18
WHEREAS, Rickenbacker is located within four hours of 60% 19
of all Department of Defense customers and six to eight hours of 20

